<mainText attr1="Targeting Overview:"/>
<mainText attr1="Targeting objects can be done in a variety of ways. The simplest is to left click on the object. Because targeting hostile ships is much more important, these functions have key bindings (see keys above). Repeatedly pressing the key will cycle to the next nearest."/>
